# CJK font files for the PDF Mail Merge pipeline.
#
# These are intentionally NOT committed:
#   - Noto Sans CJK is ~5-17 MB per weight and bloats clones.
#   - The runtime auto-downloads to OS tmpdir on first use and caches
#     there for subsequent renders (see lib/pdf/cjk-font.ts).
#
# If you want offline / air-gapped builds, drop the file at:
#   lib/pdf/fonts/NotoSansCJK-Regular.otf
# Get it from:
#   https://github.com/notofonts/noto-cjk/raw/165c01b/Sans/OTF/TraditionalChinese/NotoSansCJKtc-Regular.otf
# The loader checks this path first, so committed bundles always win
# over the CDN cache.

*.otf
*.ttf
*.ttc
*.woff
*.woff2

# But DO commit this .gitignore so the directory exists in fresh clones.
!.gitignore
